## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources reviewed. Some sources may reflect personal opinions rather than empirical research. Additionally, the implementation of sign language education may vary significantly by region, affecting the generalizability of the findings. Further research could explore case studies of schools that have successfully integrated sign language into their curricula.